{"tid":2161122,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【具有中國特色社會主義的搶劫劫案】不搶銀行 搶豬肉 - 肉價太高 廣西五名男子持凶器搶走七十頭豬","createTime":"2020-08-17T11:26:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T00:35:44.000Z","uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dcc6bd85b57299b3d116611e4e6ec9ceca5ba783","tid":2161122,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:26:30.000Z","msg":"廣西來賓市武宣縣一家養豬場日前被5名男子持鋼管搶走70頭種豬，價值13萬餘元人民幣，目前這5人已經被拘留。<br />\n<br />\n據嫌犯韋某表示，因今年以來豬肉價格飛漲，他們偷養豬場還未長大的種豬來賣錢。而且在今年1月和5月還搶、盜種豬共109頭。<br />\n<br />\n大陸豬肉價格近來持續上漲。據中共農業農村部畜牧獸醫局對全國500個縣集貿市場的定點監測，大陸豬肉平均價格從5月份第4周的45.98元/公斤，連續漲至7月份第5周的55.50元/公斤。<br />\n<br />\n而中共統計局8月10日的數據稱，7月CPI同比上漲2.7%，其中豬肉價格同比上漲85.7%，6月至7月期間，豬肉價格上漲了10.3%。<br />\n<br />\n有多名業內人士認為，當前大陸生豬產業總體供需關係仍然偏緊，而中共農業農村部有關負責人表示，下半年豬肉價格再繼續大幅上漲的可能性不大。<br />\n<br />\n有網民對此表示，農業農村部的意思是肉價還會漲啊。<br />\n<br />\n很多網民對豬肉價格不停上漲表示了不滿，網民「陳宏國」表示：「豬肉作為餐桌上不可或缺的物品，60元/公斤的高價位叫人有些抓狂&hellip;&hellip;」「甚麼漲價，壓根就沒有便宜過。」<br />\n<br />\n「城市搜索」表示：「掌控著豬肉進口調劑的企業是肯定不缺豬肉的！他們缺的是良心、良知！看看這些企業上半年的利潤報告就知道了！他們這些企業，都是幾十億上百億的利潤。」<br />\n<br />\n大連網民小祁表示：「這就是（中共）管控的結果。」"},{"pid":"88fc4138854da72d67f3cb1fa52f89dceb569bec","tid":2161122,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:26:59.000Z","msg":"唔係最紅嘅youtuber好快就開審<br />\n你會理佢嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2161113\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2161113</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c6f74f094a6df8c799dd479b674d118487cbabe6","tid":2161122,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:27:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/a72bafd4ef720078230c051961f7d695a5d4f329.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.hdslb.com%2Fbfs%2Farchive%2Fa72bafd4ef720078230c051961f7d695a5d4f329.jpg&h=55f67463&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7f3c7f4234edc5b69e460ef872d05320fd0554f","tid":2161122,"uid":156936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:33:07.000Z","msg":"個環境要幾差先寧願搶70隻豬都唔走去銀行搶錢？<br />\n<br />\n就係銀行捲款跑路，糧食商店限購，食店n-2，城市失業通漲，糧田大稻水浸<br />\n<br />\n有錢買唔起豬肉"},{"pid":"804c8b7918a0341b5ac02e4b4ae1a2c3e777bfdb","tid":2161122,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:33:44.000Z","msg":"豬： <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4889b51fe69a6b6e9dc170bdc0b79bfb8ea40938","tid":2161122,"uid":278298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:34:27.000Z","msg":"人民幣會貶值，豬肉日日升值<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a099cb0e9d3ea03a180b07930e380208d48e8c","tid":2161122,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"804c8b7918a0341b5ac02e4b4ae1a2c3e777bfdb","tid":2161122,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:33:44.000Z","msg":"豬： <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:34:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0d4a42f549645945b21cc39aa4507f971c6d82","tid":2161122,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4889b51fe69a6b6e9dc170bdc0b79bfb8ea40938","tid":2161122,"uid":278298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:34:27.000Z","msg":"人民幣會貶值，豬肉日日升值<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/d